<entry thead="yes"><para>mode   </para>
</entry><entry thead="yes"><para>м„ӨлӘ…    </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>SINGLE_TEXT_VISUALIZER</computeroutput>   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>н•ҳлӮҳмқҳ <computeroutput>TextVisualizer</computeroutput>к°Җ м „мІҙ grid textлҘј л ҢлҚ”л§Ғн•ңлӢӨ. л§Ө frame м „мІҙ text stringмқ„ л§Ңл“Өкі  hashк°Җ л°”лҖҗ кІҪмҡ°м—җл§Ң <computeroutput>SetText()</computeroutput>лҘј нҳём¶ңн•ңлӢӨ.    </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>PARTIAL_TEXT_VISUALIZER_TILES</computeroutput>   </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>кё°мЎҙ Label tile мғҳн”ҢмІҳлҹј gridлҘј tileлЎң лӮҳлҲҲлӢӨ. dirty tileл§Ң textлҘј rebuildн•ҳкі  н•ҙлӢ№ tile <computeroutput>TextVisualizer</computeroutput>м—җ <computeroutput>SetText()</computeroutput>лҘј нҳём¶ңн•ңлӢӨ.   </para>
</entry></row>
</table>
</para>
<para><computeroutput>5</computeroutput> keyлЎң л‘җ modeлҘј м „нҷҳн•ңлӢӨ.</para>
